<view class="screen stack">
  <view class="hero-panel stack">
    <text class="eyebrow">绑定设备</text>
    <text class="hero-title">输入绑定码，把设备接进这台小程序工作台</text>
    <text class="hero-copy">P0 先用绑定码完成归属建立，后续再扩展更多设备识别与批量管理能力。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section stack">
    <view class="field">
      <text class="label">绑定码</text>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入设备绑定码" value="{{bindingCode}}" bindinput="onBindingCodeInput" />
    </view>
    <view class="chip-row">
      <text class="chip">设备归属</text>
      <text class="chip">状态同步</text>
      <text class="chip">任务下发</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="primary-btn" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="submit">确认绑定</button>
</view>
